.Sh NOTES
.Fn BIO_next
was added to OpenSSL 0.9.6 to provide a 'clean' way to traverse a BIO
chain or find multiple matches using
.Fn BIO_find_type .
Previous versions had to use:
.Pp
.Dl next = bio->next_bio;
@


